<i>noun</i>: 요망 [요망], 소홀 [소홀], 불찰 [불찰], 부주의 [부주의/부주이], 방심 [방ː심], 경망 [경망] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>요망 [요망]</dt><br>
<dd>1. cunningness; slyness</dd><br>
<dd>간사하고 영악함.</dd><br>
<dd>The trait of being crafty and vicious.</dd><br>
<dd>2. carelessness; recklessness</dd><br>
<dd>말과 행동 등이 점잖지 못하고 가벼움.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of not being well-mannered but being frivolous in one's speech, behavior, etc.</dd><br>
<dt>소홀 [소홀]</dt><br>
<dd>carelessness; negligence; indifference</dd><br>
<dd>중요하게 생각하지 않아 주의나 정성이 부족함.</dd><br>
<dd>A lack of care or caution about something because one does not think it is important.</dd><br>
<dt>불찰 [불찰]</dt><br>
<dd>carelessness; negligence; fault</dd><br>
<dd>주의를 기울여 조심하지 않은 탓으로 저지른 잘못.</dd><br>
<dd>A mistake made due to lack of attention or caution.</dd><br>
<dt>부주의 [부주의/부주이]</dt><br>
<dd>carelessness</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일을 하는 데에 정신을 집중하지 않아 조심스럽지 않음.</dd><br>
<dd>A state of paying little attention to something and thus being not careful.</dd><br>
<dt>방심 [방ː심]</dt><br>
<dd>carelessness; sloppiness</dd><br>
<dd>긴장하거나 조심하지 않고 마음을 놓음.</dd><br>
<dd>The quality of not being prudent or careful, but being off guard, letting one's guard down.</dd><br>
<dt>경망 [경망]</dt><br>
<dd>flippancy; frivolity; carelessness; hastiness; imprudence</dd><br>
<dd>말이나 행동이 가볍고 조심스럽지 못함.</dd><br>
<dd>A remark or behavior being light and careless.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>